name: SakimiChan Art Style
description:
This LoRA will help create images in SakimiChan's style.

For better use, You need to install Addition Network Extension

Installation

  1. Open "Extensions" tab.

  2. Open "Install from URL" tab in the tab.

  3. Enter https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks.git to "URL for extension's git repository".

  4. Press "Install" button.

  5. Restart Web UI.

How to use this Lora

  1. Dowload

  2. Place this Lora in stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora\

  3. After Installed Additional Networks you will see this section below Seed text Box

  4. Click refresh models to load Lora

  5. Tick Enable

  6. Choose LoRA in Network module 1, Choose Lora Name in Model 1

  7. Adjust the Weight at Weight 1

More Information

  1. Using with my Model for best result: https://civitai.com/models/73945/nova-ai-art-v1

  2. Have a look at my other Lora: https://civitai.com/user/chuong1224/models

  3. My Others page: https://linktr.ee/NovaAIArt
